{"id":"806352462429765632","type":"text","timestamp":1768997633,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/806352462429765632","is_reblog":true,"added_content":true,"tags":["50 reblogs","tumblr milestone","thank you"],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/806288166015369216\">goodtransgirl</a>:</p><blockquote><p>I hug her goodbye, but neither of us is ready to release the other immediately. It’s not long enough to be dramatic, but long enough to communicate to the other, &ldquo;Please stay! Somehow!&rdquo; When we finally pull apart, we both take a tiny step back, as if distance might help. We look deeply in each others eyes and any assistance that came with the slight distance fades. I take her hand, kiss it, and say goodbye, then with so much effort, I turn away, not letting her hand drop from mine, savoring as much touch as possible, until she is too far for my arm to reach. And my mind whispers, <i>Soon&hellip;</i></p></blockquote>\n<div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"880\" data-orig-width=\"1080\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d55b17d65d3a916e9973889645d4fa7a/b204679cf1d29b4f-02/s640x960/a3ca19a8e88603777d4c2b96f62469058d94b66c.png\" data-orig-height=\"880\" data-orig-width=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d55b17d65d3a916e9973889645d4fa7a/b204679cf1d29b4f-02/s75x75_c1/c328a0d09a5351c8e93b634e83f2405ac2d93d81.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d55b17d65d3a916e9973889645d4fa7a/b204679cf1d29b4f-02/s100x200/3a9353abb16736919299434506f54d7d7347eb6a.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d55b17d65d3a916e9973889645d4fa7a/b204679cf1d29b4f-02/s250x400/f2572a6b30be1e0571368f04a011e4e8aaee7810.png 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d55b17d65d3a916e9973889645d4fa7a/b204679cf1d29b4f-02/s400x600/56bc0a6f941811073acd3e6df2d2e90d310ef1ec.png 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d55b17d65d3a916e9973889645d4fa7a/b204679cf1d29b4f-02/s500x75